OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer Grace Thomas
OL,9,FSteve Hilton, a British-born
OL,10,Fpolitician, has secured a spot in the
OL,11,Frace to become California's next
OL,12,Fgovernor.
OL,14,FThe 56-year-old Republican - backed by
OL,15,FDonald Trump - will face Democrat
OL,16,FXavier Becerra, who was Joe Biden's
OL,17,Fhealth and human services secretary,
OL,18,Fin the November mid-term election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
