OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781121970
OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FThe winner will succeed Democratic
OL,8,FGovernor Gavin Newsom, and lead the
OL,9,Fstate that is home to roughly 39
OL,10,Fmillion people.
OL,12,FBut who is Hilton and what makes him
OL,13,Fan unusual candidate? ITV News
OL,14,Fexplains.
OL,16,FWhat is Hilton's background?
OL,18,FSteve Hilton was born in England to
OL,19,FHungarian parents, who were refugees
OL,20,Ffrom communism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
