OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FHe studied at Oxford University before
OL,8,Fgetting a job with the Conservative
OL,9,FParty when Margaret Thatcher was prime
OL,10,Fminister.
OL,12,FHe then made a career in business and
OL,13,Fopened restaurants in London before
OL,14,Fgetting back into politics.
OL,16,FHilton served as a top aide to former
OL,17,FPrime Minister David Cameron from 2010
OL,18,Fto 2012, where he gained a reputation
OL,19,Ffor his unconventional fashion
OL,20,Fchoices, including walking around
OL,21,FNumber 10 without shoes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
