OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781121970
OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FHis laid-back approach even prompted
OL,8,Fthe American embassy to explicitly
OL,9,Frequire him to wear shoes and socks
OL,10,Fduring a state visit from then-
OL,11,FPresident Barack Obama in 2011.
OL,13,FHilton was the architect of Cameron's
OL,14,FBig Society policy, which aimed to
OL,15,Fshift power from central government to
OL,16,Flocal communities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
