OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FDespite being one of Cameron's closest
OL,8,Fadvisors, the pair fell out over
OL,9,FBrexit after Hilton warned it would be
OL,10,F"impossible" to meet the government's
OL,11,Fpledge on immigration if Britain
OL,12,Fstayed in the EU.
OL,14,FWhen did he move to the US?
OL,16,FHilton quit Downing Street and moved
OL,17,Fto California in 2012 with his tech
OL,18,Fexecutive wife, Rachel Whetstone, to
OL,19,Fteach at California's Stanford
OL,20,FUniversity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
