OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FIn 2017, he began a six-year stint
OL,8,Fhosting a television show, The Next
OL,9,FRevolution, on the conservative news
OL,10,Fnetwork, Fox News.
OL,12,FHe became a US citizen in 2021.
OL,14,FWhat does he stand for?
OL,16,FHilton may be an outsider in the
OL,17,Felection, but he's embracing it,
OL,18,Fclaiming the momentum behind his
OL,19,Fcampaign shows voters are sick of the
OL,20,FDemocratic status quo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
