OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FHe has focused his campaign on
OL,8,Faffordability issues, promising to
OL,9,Fmake Californians' first $100,000
OL,10,F(around #74,600) free of income tax,
OL,11,Fcreate a loan programme for first-time
OL,12,Fhomebuyers, and freeze in-state
OL,13,Ftuition at public colleges.
OL,15,F"If you're happy with the way that
OL,16,FCalifornia is being run, Xavier
OL,17,FBecerra is your guy," Hilton said in a
OL,18,Frecent interview with the Associated
OL,19,FPress, "If you want change, vote for
OL,20,Fme."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
