OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FWhat is his relationship like with
OL,8,FPresident Trump?
OL,10,FHilton has already been endorsed by
OL,11,FTrump, who called him a "great
OL,12,Fgovernor" in a Truth Social post in
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FThe president claimed that "Democrats
OL,16,Fhave done an absolutely horrendous
OL,17,Fjob" in California and "people are
OL,18,Ffleeing" the state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
