OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FAt the time, Hilton said that he was
OL,8,F"deeply honoured" to receive the
OL,9,Fpresident's endorsement.
OL,11,FBut he has since tried to distance
OL,12,Fhimself from some of Trump's more
OL,13,Fcontroversial claims that the
OL,14,FCalifornia elections are "rigged".
OL,16,FIt took nearly a week to determine the
OL,17,Fgeneral election matchup for governor
OL,18,Fdue to California's notoriously slow
OL,19,Fvote-counting process.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
