OL,3,CWho is Steve Hilton, the ex-Downing
OL,4,CStreet aide running for California
OL,5,Cgovernor?
OL,7,FHilton told CNN's Erin Burnett last
OL,8,Fweek that he has "seen nothing" to
OL,9,Fjustify intervening in the election.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FWhat are his chances of winning?
OL,18,FHilton faces a challenging electorate
OL,19,Fin the election, as California has
OL,20,Fnearly twice as many registered
OL,21,FDemocratic voters as Republicans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
